Laundry Service Hero Section

Project Description
This project is a simple frontend layout for a laundry service website. It includes a navbar and a hero section with a call-to-action button.

How to Run
1. Download the project
2. Open index.html in browser

What I Learned
- How to use Flexbox for layout
- How viewport units (vh, vw) work
- How to align elements properly

Challenges Faced
- Initially struggled with spacing between text and image
- Image alignment was not correct
- Fixed it by adjusting flex properties and width

Improvements
- Added hover effects to navbar and button
